Rice is a type of food that can be cooked, so the intent is cooking.

Positive Exmples.input: please set alarm for all days

Negative Exmples.input: notify me when trump is in the news
Negative Exmples.explanation: The intent is asking for an update on the news, not transportaion. The intent is news.
The text is not about alarms, but transportation. The intent is transport.

Negative Exmples.input: have i set any alarms in the morning

Negative Exmples.input: can you order me some buffalo chicken pizza
